title: Hour 1 - Monday Night Football Reaction, Dan Le Batard
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Monday Night Football Reaction, Dan Le Batard
description:
Dan reacts to the unimpressive Monday Night Football game where an average Cowboys QB (Cooper Rush) outplayed a below average Giants QB (Daniel Jones). And Dan Le Batard drops by to crow about his Miami Dolphins.
